{"type":"message","id":"64f1c1e4","parentId":"9b4ebc5d","timestamp":"2026-04-15T06:28:50.818Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture. Let me analyze the active sessions (excluding this cron session):\n\n1. **agent:master-orchestrator:cron:ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7** — \"Cron: 5p Progress Report\" (QLHV) — running — ~2h 32m\n2. **agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31** — \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\" — running — ~1h 17m\n3. **agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:group:-5163901258** — \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - QLHV Group\" — running — the session started at 1776163408296 (Apr 15 03:23 UTC?) but ended at 1776163783190 (~6 min runtime). Status is \"running\" but it ended. This is the QLHV Telegram group session.\n\n\n4. **agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134** — Lead Direct — done (~17s runtime)\n5. **agent:master-orchestrator:main** — main — done (~15s runtime)\n\nLooking more carefully at the group session, the \"endedAt\" timestamp and \"runtimeMs\" of 8014ms confirm it actually terminated. The \"running\" status appears to be misleading, possibly reflecting the session was marked as running when it last sent a message, but it did complete.\n\nFor the status report, I'll report only sessions that are genuinely active with an actual \"running\" status, excluding this cron job and the Lead Direct session which is already done. That leaves the two cron sessions. Now I need to calculate their durations based on the session timestamps. The Lead Direct session ended normally, so there's no change there either. I'm realizing the duration calculations might be slightly off since I'm working with integer math on timestamps, but I can work around that by looking at the updatedAt values to cross-check the actual runtimes. Now I'm formatting the status report with the three active cron jobs—two monitoring pipelines and one agent status check—along with their durations, ready to send to the Lead Direct session.","thinkingSignature":"3de45bf8e927263e301012a7ba7105db0bf52e7c4273467564adf09b38916b45"},{"type":"text","text":"Active sessions identified. Now compiling and sending the report to Lead.\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jgh3e61768pr_1","name":"sessions_send","arguments":{"sessionKey":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","message":"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 06:27 UTC 15 Apr\n\nActive sessions: 3\n• 5p Progress Report (QLHV): running — Pipeline stability check (5min cadence) — ~2h 32m\n• 5p Progress Report - DTLX: running — Pipeline stability check (5min cadence) — ~1h 17m\n• Agent Status to Lead: running — Heartbeat cron (15min cadence) — ~14m"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":3156,"output":642,"cacheRead":14084,"cacheWrite":3395,"totalTokens":21277,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776234509188,"responseId":"062e630d7b218c91cb32e2816816830b"}}
